-------MVC:
How to create:
1. We need to add View(HTTPs/frontend)
----> create file with the extension of .jsp
-----> JSP support both HTTML and java.
-----> src/main/weapp/WEB-INF/view/file.jsp
2.  We need to add the dependency for JSP file.
----tomcat jasper mvn
---->jstl mvn
3. We need to inform Spring that where is our JSP file locate
----->app.xml


